Time Train No. Print this Page Shanghai - Hangzhou Train Schedule Departing toFrom Owing to the close location to Hangzhou, it is very convenient to travel to Hangzhou from Shanghai by train. Many trains are scheduled to go to Hangzhou from Shanghai every day, and most of them depart from Shanghai Hongqiao Railway Station and Shanghai South Railway Station. China Highlights provides a Shanghai-Hangzhou train schedule, and passengers can search for a suitable train from Shanghai to Hangzhou. Taking a train tour to Hangzhou from Shanghai is convenient owing to the well-developed rail network. China Highlights can help you with Shanghai-Hangzhou train schedule.
